Started in the US in 2006, <a href="https://www.bcorporation.net/">B Corp</a> has spread around the world and, as of October 2023, there are now over **7,300 B Corps** operating in 93 countries and 161 industries. The B Corp certification is managed by B Lab, a global nonprofit organization. It is founded on the belief that the power of business can be harnessed as a force for good with the right guidance and influence.

