### B Corp and the .eco registry

Prior to launching .eco, we were proud to be one of the first B Corporations in Canada. Moreover, B Lab representatives played a valuable role on the [.eco Stakeholder Council](https://org.eco/) – the group of organizations who helped develop the consensus on .eco’s mission and values.

In our [2023 Impact Plan](https://go.eco/news/2022-impact-report/), we set a goal of recertifying as a B Corp this year. We are currently in the evaluation stage and are looking forward to rejoining the B Corporation community. Stay tuned!
